						               													<description>This is a free PnP Game designed for the 2020 Solitaire PnP Contest.  Assets available in the files link.***&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You are the General Manager of a new American Football team who needs to sign all 22 starters to your roster while staying under budget.  Build a balanced championship level team and win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All players are on individual mini playing cards and have a preferred salary &amp;amp; stat scores for 10 critical football traits like passing, blocking, &amp;amp; tackling.  When deciding to sign a player, you place them into a starting spot on the game board which values 3 of the 10 traits. The player's scores will generate one of 4 types of victory points (Toughness, Explosiveness, Intelligence and Skill).  You win by keeping these 4 victory point totals in balance while assembling a skillful team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With a salary cap of $500MM, you need to decide who to sign, how much to pay &amp;amp; what they will contribute to your overall team.  Do you have the vision needed to assemble a champion?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Designed by Joe Fontana (Formulaic Games)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
